emary cream dressing" title="Beef fillet with fennel salad &amp; rosemary cream dressing" /></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> <a href="/recipes/2536/beef-fillet-with-fennel-salad-and-rosemary-cream-d"> Beef fillet with fennel salad &amp; rosemary cream dressing </a></h3><div class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-form-item"><div class="form-item form-type-item"><div class="field-main"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">5</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="description"><p class="fivestar-summary fivestar-summary-">(1<span class="rating-text"> rating</span>)</p></div></div></div></div></div> </article></li><li class=""><article id="node-93569" class="node node-recipe node-carousel-slide-narrow clearfix"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_small/public/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--2426_12.jpg?itok=k19Apdkq" width="324" height="294" alt="Marinated barbecue lamb with shallot marmalade, served with griddled vegetables" title="Marinated barbecue lamb with shallot marmalade, served with griddled vegetables" /></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> <a href="/recipes/2224/marinated-barbecue-lamb-with-shallot-marmalade-ser"> Marinated barbecue lamb with shallot marmalade, served with griddled vegetables </a></h3><div class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-form-item"><div class="form-item form